TY  - JOUR
T1  - What happened to the oil price-macroeconomy relationship?
AU  - Hooker, Mark A.
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 38
IS  - 2
SP  - 195
EP  - 213
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/10/01/
SN  - 0304-3932
