T1  - Innovation, bank monitoring, and endogenous financial development
AU  - de la Fuente, Angel
AU  - Marín, JoséMaría
JO  - Journal of Monetary Economics
VL  - 38
IS  - 2
SP  - 269
EP  - 301
PY  - 1996
DA  - 1996/10/01/
SN  - 0304-3932
